en_114218_0	Transport Minister Ranjith Madduma Bandara states that legal action will be taken against former President Mahinda Rajapaksa for not paying the fees for SLTB buses that were used for the previous presidential election.
en_114218_1	Addressing a meeting held in Monaragala, Minister Ranjith Madduma Bandara stated that 192.5 million rupees are yet to be paid for the SLTB.
